for when I know someone has donated an

00:02:01.259 --> 00:02:05.399
organ. For me it does have a lot of
personal significance because I've had

00:02:05.399 --> 00:02:08.910
family members who have been touched by transplant. but it also it just

00:02:08.910 --> 00:02:13.980
